    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>This recipe takes around 5-10 min to prep, so get your casserole dish and all your ingredients ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Make sure your dish is oven-proof and safe to use on the hob. Don't have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish and cover tightly with foil</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based,<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> lime[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped shallot </strong>and<strong> chopped pepper</strong> to the dish</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> </strong>your<strong> roasted garlic paste </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>smoky stock</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to the dish with your<strong> basmati rice</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> smoky stock </strong>with your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, top with your <strong>hake fillet[s] </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the rice is cooked and the fish is cooked through \u2013 this is your <strong>one pot hake & Mexican-style rice</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime quarters </strong>with a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>\u2013 this is your<strong> lime mayo</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-hake-and-mexican-style-rice-with-lime-mayo/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one pot hake & Mexican-style rice </strong>and drizzle over the<strong> lime mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and a <strong>remaining lime quarter</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
